l M. Highsmith's America Project in the Carol M. Highsmith Archive, Library of Congress, Prints and Photographs Division."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2022-08-02T18:21:30.504Z", "group": ["catalog", "highsm", "catalog-split-02", "main-catalog", "carol-m-highsmith", "main-catalog-split-02"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021756308/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/pnp/highsm/68000/68087_150px.jpg#h=150&w=120", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/pnp/highsm/68000/68087r.jpg#h=640&w=513", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/pnp/highsm/68000/68087v.jpg#h=1024&w=821"], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "south dakota", "davison county", "mitchell"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/jpg", "image/tif"], "number": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/22635827", "2021756308", "online resource", "2022-06-09t14:46:20"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["photo, print, drawing"], "partof": ["catalog", "highsmith (carol m.) archive", "prints and photographs division", "prints & photographs online catalog (library of congress)"], "score": 43.03881, "shelf_id": "LC-DIG-highsm- 68087", "site": ["catalog", "pictures"], "subject": ["south dakota attractions", "south dakota", "digital photographs", "corn palace", "united states", "america", "color", "davison county", "mitchell"], "timestamp": "2022-08-02T18:31:54.690Z", "title": "A corner of the Corn Palace, an arena and event venue that is one of Midwest America's most popular tourist attractions (whose advertising makes it clear that it's the world's ONLY corn palace), in the small city of Mitchell, South Dakota", "type": ["still image"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021756308/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/2021756309", "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021756309/", "https://hdl.loc.gov/loc.pnp/highsm.68088", "http://www.loc.gov/resource/highsm.68088/", "https://www.loc.gov/pictu